  <section xml:id="loggerpropertyconfigurator.intro">
   &reftitle.intro;
   <para>
    Before logging anything from your program you need to configure the log4cxx. This is
    done through a properties file. Instructions on how to write a log4j.property file can be
    found <link xlink:href="&url.log4cxx;">here</link>.
    Place the configuration file into a place readable by php and then use the configure method
    to load the configuration into log4cxx.
   </para>
